[{"id":747316,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1610122510","description":"<p>1.用的代码是别的项目 copy 过来的，换了个字段就不会正则校验了，问他传过去文件了那边更新数据库了没，他说还在百度查正则表达式。\n2.写接口不写文档，直接微信甩个接口名，问他传什么参数他自己都说不清楚，让我自己传着试试。\n3.测试接口的时候时不时的重启服务，我这边直接崩溃。\n4.因为他描述不清楚数据导致我写代码的困难，竟然质问我为啥还调不通接口。\n难以想象这是三年经验 java 工程师。。。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/747316","replies":128,"created_ts":1611285297,"created":"11:14:57","title":"项目组搭档的后端实在太不专业，几次都差点忍不住想之间当他面说出来吐槽","author":"littlechichen","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/littlechichen","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/991f/621d/379848_mini.png?m=1611302833"},{"id":747298,"node":"职场话题","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/career","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1608179815","description":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/747298","replies":116,"created_ts":1611283008,"created":"10:36:48","title":"怎么看待,工作满一年了,涨了 500 薪资？","author":"VVVV7","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/VVVV7","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/8d466cc74fe2b112009d89e2a7ed371c?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":747319,"node":"分享创造","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/create","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_mini.png?m=1596015931","description":"数独游戏还是很好玩的<br /><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://github.com/myth984/sudoku\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://github.com/myth984/sudoku</a>","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/747319","replies":91,"created_ts":1611285448,"created":"11:17:28","title":"整了个多人在线数独游戏","author":"mythjava","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/mythjava","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4b14/8cad/420605_mini.png?m=1577326242"},{"id":747246,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1594743680","description":"<p>我先来，南京，某私企，目前没有任何补贴消息。[狗头]</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://baijiahao.baidu.com/s?id=1689476961059028159\" rel=\"nof